C-365 September Term 2017
079862 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 1, 2017

In the MATTER OF the CIVIL COMMITMENT OF P.P., SVP-711-15.

(P.P.-Petitioner)

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004011-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
